c: 10
v: 21
t: "N’iyo dusogongeje abantu ku mpuhwe (zacu) nyuma y’amakuba yabagezeho, bacurira imigambi mibisha amagambo yacu. Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Allah ni ubanguka mu kuburizamo imigambi mibisha.” Mu by’ukuri intumwa zacu (abamalayika) zandika imigambi mibisha yanyu (hanyuma tukazabakurikirana)"